    <title type="html"><![CDATA[SASS better box-shadow mixin]]></title>
    <link href="http://brousalis.com/blog/2012/07/01/sass-better-box-shadow-mixin/"/>
    <updated>2012-07-01T13:12:00-05:00</updated>
    <id>http://brousalis.com/blog/2012/07/01/sass-better-box-shadow-mixin</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>I&#8217;ve seen a similar box-shadow mixin in several places, particularly <a href="http://twitter.github.com/bootstrap">Twitter Bootstrap</a>, and I think it can be improved.</p>

<figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='sass'><span class='line'><span class="k">@mixin</span><span class="nf"> box-shadow</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nv">$shadow</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="err">{</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="na">-webkit-box-shadow</span><span class="o">:</span> <span class="nv">$shadow</span><span class="err">;</span>
</span><span class='line'>     <span class="na">-moz-box-shadow</span><span class="o">:</span> <span class="nv">$shadow</span><span class="err">;</span>
</span><span class='line'>          <span class="na">box-shadow</span><span class="o">:</span> <span class="nv">$shadow</span><span class="err">;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="err">}</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>This is the mixin most often seen, however it doesn&#8217;t allow for multiple shadows, like:</p>

<figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='css'><span class='line'><span class="nt">box-shadow</span><span class="o">:</span> <span class="nt">0</span> <span class="nt">0</span> <span class="nt">2px</span> <span class="nt">rgba</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="nt">0</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="nt">0</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="nt">0</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="nc">.1</span><span class="o">),</span> <span class="nt">0</span> <span class="nt">2px</span> <span class="nt">5px</span> <span class="nt">rgba</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="nt">0</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="nt">0</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="nt">0</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="nc">.2</span><span class="o">)</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>Here is my modified version that supports multiple shadows:</p>

<figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='sass'><span class='line'><span class="k">@mixin</span><span class="nf"> box-shadow</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nv">$shadow1</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="nv">$shadow2</span><span class="o">:</span><span class="n-Pseudo">false</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="nv">$shadow3</span><span class="o">:</span><span class="n-Pseudo">false</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="err">{</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="nv">$shadows</span><span class="o">:</span> <span class="nv">$shadow1</span><span class="err">;</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="k">@if</span> <span class="nv">$shadow2</span> <span class="err">{</span> <span class="nv">$shadows</span><span class="o">:</span> <span class="nv">$shadow1</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="nv">$shadow2</span><span class="err">;</span> <span class="err">}</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="k">@if</span> <span class="nv">$shadows</span> <span class="o">!=</span> <span class="n-Pseudo">false</span> <span class="err">{</span> <span class="nv">$shadows</span><span class="o">:</span> <span class="nv">$shadow1</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="nv">$shadow2</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="nv">$shadow3</span><span class="err">;</span> <span class="err">}</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="na">-webkit-box-shadow</span><span class="o">:</span> <span class="nv">$shadows</span><span class="err">;</span>
</span><span class='line'>     <span class="na">-moz-box-shadow</span><span class="o">:</span> <span class="nv">$shadows</span><span class="err">;</span>
</span><span class='line'>          <span class="na">box-shadow</span><span class="o">:</span> <span class="nv">$shadows</span><span class="err">;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="err">}</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>You can then call it:</p>

<figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='css'><span class='line'><span class="k">@include</span> <span class="nt">box-shadow</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="nt">0</span> <span class="nt">0</span> <span class="nt">2px</span> <span class="nt">rgba</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="nt">0</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="nt">0</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="nt">0</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="nc">.1</span><span class="o">),</span> <span class="nt">0</span> <span class="nt">2px</span> <span class="nt">5px</span> <span class="nt">rgba</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="nt">0</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="nt">0</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="nt">0</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="nc">.2</span><span class="o">)</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>



]]></content>
